### Seed — admin-only operational data populator
###
### Wipes feedbacks/agent_suggestions/order_line_items/orders/documents,
### upserts retailers + suppliers from the canonical lists, uploads sample
### files (real Document rows + MinIO blobs), then generates synthetic
### historical + pending orders + suggestions + feedbacks.

@host = http://localhost:8000

# @name loginAdmin
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin123

###

# @name loginOperator
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=operator&password=operator123


# ============================================================================
# POST /api/seed — admin only
# ============================================================================

### Default counts (200 historical, 30 pending, 50 feedbacks). Takes ~10–20s.
POST {{host}}/api/seed
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### Small counts for quick iteration
POST {{host}}/api/seed?historical_count=10&pending_count=3&feedback_count=2
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### Larger counts for stress test
POST {{host}}/api/seed?historical_count=500&pending_count=100&feedback_count=200
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### As operator → 403 (admin-only)
POST {{host}}/api/seed
Authorization: Bearer {{loginOperator.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### Without a token → 401
POST {{host}}/api/seed
